An '''Encounter''' may refer to:

*[[Encounter/Sexual|Sexual encounter]], where a character can solicit, assault, ignore, or argue with a sex worker they encounter.
*[[Encounter/Animal|Animal encounter]], where a character encounters an animal and can choose to run away, walk away slowly, pet it, or rescue/adopt it as a pet.
*Enemy encounter, where an enemy confronts and attempts to assault a character with a weapon 
